user.full_name: Down to Earth with Zac Efron

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Zac Efron on July 18, 2021 tagging @netflix, and @zacdowntoearth. May be an image of 1 person, beard and text that says 'DAYTIME EMMY'AWARDS WINNER OUTSTANDING DAYTIME PROGRAM HOST DOWN TO EARTH WITH ZAC EFRON N'.

node.text:
Wow! Never expected this and so grateful.

A HUGE thank you to #daytimeemmys @netflix and our small but powerful crew @zacdowntoearth who made this show what it is.

And most of all, thank all of you for watching and enjoying D2E. This is for you. Get ready for the next adventure it’s going to be a good one. Love u guys ❤️🙏🏼
